quran[170]{c,v,t}:
  11,6,WE MA MIN DABBETIN FIL-’ERDI ‘ILLA ‘ALA ELLAHI RIZKUHA WE JA’LEMU MUSTEKARREHA WE MUSTEWDE’AHA KULLUN FI KITABIN MUBININ
  11,7,WE HUWEL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE FI SITTETI ‘EJJAMIN WE KANE ‘ARSHUHU ‘ALEL-MA’I LIJEBLUWEKUM ‘EJJUKUM ‘EHSENU ‘AMELÆN WE LE’IN KULTE ‘INNEKUM MEB’UTHUNE MIN BA’DIL-MEWTI LEJEKULENNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘IN HADHA ‘ILLA SIHRUN MUBINUN
  11,8,WE LE’IN ‘EHHARNA ‘ANHUMUL-’ADHABE ‘ILA ‘UMMETIN MA’DUDETIN LEJEKULUNNE MA JEHBISUHU ‘ELA JEWME JE’TIHIM LEJSE MESRUFÆN ‘ANHUM WE HAKA BIHIM MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  11,9,WE LE’IN ‘EDHEKNAL-’INSANE MINNA REHMETEN THUMME NEZA’NAHA MINHU ‘INNEHU LEJE’USUN KEFURUN
  11,10,WE LE’IN ‘EDHEKNAHU NA’MA’E BA’DE DERRA’E MESSET/HU LEJEKULENNE DHEHEBE ES-SEJJI’ATU ‘ANNI ‘INNEHU LEFERIHUN FEHURUN
  11,11,‘ILLAL-LEDHINE SEBERU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM MEGFIRETUN WE ‘EXHRUN KEBIRUN
  11,12,FELE’ALLEKE TARIKUN BA’DE MA JUHA ‘ILEJKE WE DA’IKUN BIHI SEDRUKE ‘EN JEKULU LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJHI KENZUN ‘EW XHA’E ME’AHU MELEKUN ‘INNEMA ‘ENTE NEDHIRUN WEL-LAHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN WE KILUN
  11,13,‘EM JEKULUNE EFTERAHU KUL FE’TU BI’ASHRI SUWERIN MITHLIHI MUFTEREJATIN WE ED’U MENI ESTETA’TUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  11,14,FE’ILLEM JESTEXHIBU LEKUM FA’LEMU ‘ENNEMA ‘UNZILE BI’ILMI ELLAHI WE ‘EN LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE FEHEL ‘ENTUM MUSLIMUNE
  11,15,MEN KANE JURIDUL-HEJÆTE ED-DUNJA WE ZINETEHA NUWEFFI ‘ILEJHIM ‘A’MALEHUM FIHA WE HUM FIHA LA JUBHASUNE
  11,16,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE LEJSE LEHUM FIL-’AHIRETI ‘ILLA EN-NARU WE HEBITE MA SENA’U FIHA WE BATILUN MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  11,17,‘EFEMEN KANE ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MIN RABBIHI WE JETLUHU SHAHIDUN MINHU WE MIN KABLIHI KITABU MUSA ‘IMAMÆN WE REHMETEN ‘ULA’IKE JU’UMINUNE BIHI WE MEN JEKFUR BIHI MINEL-’EHZABI FALNNARU MEW’IDUHU FELA TEKUN FI MIRJETIN MINHU ‘INNEHUL-HEKKU MIN RABBIKE WE LEKIN
  11,18,WE MEN ‘EDHLEMU MIMMENI EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN ‘ULA’IKE JU’REDUNE ‘ALA RABBIHIM WE JEKULUL-’ESH/HADU HA’UULA’L-LEDHINE KEDHEBU ‘ALA RABBIHIM ‘ELA LA’NETU ELLAHI ‘ALA EDH-DHALIMINE
  11,19,EL-LEDHINE JESUDDUNE ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI WE JEBGUNEHA ‘IWEXHÆN WE HUM BIL-’AHIRETI HUM KAFIRUNE
  11,20,‘ULA’IKE LEM JEKUNU MU’XHIZINE FIL-’ERDI WE MA KANE LEHUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI MIN ‘EWLIJA’E JUDA’AFU LEHUMUL-’ADHABU MA KANU JESTETI’UNE ES-SEM’A WE MA KANU JUBSIRUNE
  11,21,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE HASIRU ‘ENFUSEHUM WE DELLE ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEFTERUNE
  11,22,LA XHEREME ‘ENNEHUM FIL-’AHIRETI HUMUL-’EHSERUNE
  11,23,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI WE ‘EHBETU ‘ILA RABBIHIM ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABUL-XHENNETI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  11,24,METHELUL-FERIKAJNI KAL’A’MA WEL-’ESEMMI WEL-BESIRI WE ES-SEMI’I HEL JESTEWIJANI METHELÆN ‘EFELA TEDHEKKERUNE
  11,25,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA NUHÆN ‘ILA KAWMIHI ‘INNI LEKUM NEDHIRUN MUBINUN
  11,26,‘EN LA TA’BUDU ‘ILLALLAHE ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘ALEJKUM ‘ADHABE JEWMIN ‘ELIMIN
  11,27,FEKALEL-MELE’UL-LEDHINE KEFERU MIN KAWMIHI MA NERAKE ‘ILLA BESHERÆN MITHLENA WE MA NERAKE ETTEBE’AKE ‘ILLAL-LEDHINE HUM ‘ERADHILUNA BADIJE ER-RE’JI WE MA NERA LEKUM ‘ALEJNA MIN FEDLIN BEL NEDHUNNUKUM KADHIBINE
  11,28,KALE JA KAWMI ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN KUNTU ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MIN RABBI WE ‘ATANI REHMETEN MIN ‘INDIHI FA’UMMIJET ‘ALEJKUM ‘ENULZIMUKUMUHA WE ‘ENTUM LEHA KARIHUNE
  11,29,WE JAKAWMI LA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI MALÆN ‘IN ‘EXHRIJE ‘ILLA ‘ALA ELLAHI WE MA ‘ENA BITARIDIL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘INNEHUM MULAKU RABBIHIM WE LEKINNI ‘ERAKUM KAWMÆN TEXHHELUNE
  11,30,WE JAKAWMI MEN JENSURUNI MINEL-LAHI ‘IN TEREDTUHUM ‘EFELA TEDHEKKERUNE
  11,31,WE LA ‘EKULU LEKUM ‘INDI HAZA’INU ELLAHI WE LA ‘A’LEMUL-GAJBE WE LA ‘EKULU ‘INNI MELEKUN WE LA ‘EKULU LILLEDHINE TEZDERI ‘A’JUNUKUM LEN JU’UTIJEHUMU ELLAHU HAJRÆN ELLAHU ‘A’LEMU BIMA FI ‘ENFUSIHIM ‘INNI ‘IDHÆN LEMINE EDH-DHALIMINE
  11,32,KALU JA NUHU KAD XHADELTENA FE’EKTHERTE XHIDALENA FE’TINA BIMA TA’IDUNA ‘IN KUNTE MINE ES-SADIKINE
  11,33,KALE ‘INNEMA JE’TIKUM BIHI ELLAHU ‘IN SHA’E WE MA ‘ENTUM BIMU’XHIZINE
  11,34,WE LA JENFA’UKUM NUSHI ‘IN ‘EREDTU ‘EN ‘ENSEHE LEKUM ‘IN KANEL-LAHU JURIDU ‘EN JUGWIJEKUM HUWE REBBUKUM WE ‘ILEJHI TURXHA’UNE
  11,35,‘EM JEKULUNE EFTERAHU KUL ‘INI EFTEREJTUHU FE’ALEJJE ‘IXHRAMI WE ‘ENA BERI’UN MIMMA TUXHRIMUNE
  11,36,WE ‘UHIJE ‘ILA NUHIN ‘ENNEHU LEN JU’UMINE MIN KAWMIKE ‘ILLA MEN KAD ‘AMENE FELA TEBTE’IS BIMA KANU JEF’ALUNE
  11,37,WE ESNA’IL-FULKE BI’A’JUNINA WE WEHJINA WE LA TUHATIBNI FIL-LEDHINE DHELEMU ‘INNEHUM MUGREKUNE
  11,38,WE JESNA’UL-FULKE WE KULLEMA MERRE ‘ALEJHI MELE’UN MIN KAWMIHI SEHIRU MINHU KALE ‘IN TESHARU MINNA FE’INNA NESHARU MINKUM KEMA TESHARUNE
  11,39,FESEWFE TA’LEMUNE MEN JE’TIHI ‘ADHABUN JUHZIHI WE JEHILLU ‘ALEJHI ‘ADHABUN MUKIMUN
  11,40,HETTA ‘IDHA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA WE FARET-TENNURU KULNA EHMIL FIHA MIN KULLIN ZEWXHEJNI ETHNEJNI WE ‘EHLEKE ‘ILLA MEN SEBEKA ‘ALEJHIL-KAWLU WE MEN ‘AMENE WE MA ‘AMENE ME’AHU ‘ILLA KALILUN
  11,41,WE KALE ERKEBU FIHA BISMI ELLAHI MEXHRAHA WE MURSAHA ‘INNE RABBI LEGAFURUN REHIMUN
  11,42,WE HIJE TEXHRI BIHIM FI MEWXHIN KALXHIBALI WE NADA NUHUN EBNEHU WE KANE FI MA’ZILIN JA BUNEJJE ERKEB ME’ANA WE LA TEKUN ME’AL-KAFIRINE
  11,43,KALE SE’AWI ‘ILA XHEBELIN JA’SIMUNI MINEL-MA’I KALE LA ‘ASIMEL-JEWME MIN ‘EMRI ELLAHI ‘ILLA MEN REHIME WE HALE BEJNEHUMAL-MEWXHU FEKANE MINEL-MUGREKINE
  11,44,WE KILE JA ‘ERDU EBLA’I MA’EKI WE JA SEMA’U ‘EKLI’I WE GIDEL-MA’U WE KUDIJEL-’EMRU WE ESTEWET ‘ALEL-XHUDIJI WE KILE BU’DÆN LILKAWMI EDH-DHALIMINE
  11,45,WE NADA NUHUN REBBEHU FEKALE RABBI ‘INNE EBNI MIN ‘EHLI WE ‘INNE WA’DEKEL-HEKKU WE ‘ENTE ‘EHKEMUL-HAKIMINE
  11,46,KALE JA NUHU ‘INNEHU LEJSE MIN ‘EHLIKE ‘INNEHU ‘AMELUN GAJRU SALIHIN FELA TES’ELNI MA LEJSE LEKE BIHI ‘ILMUN ‘INNI ‘A’IDHUKE ‘EN TEKUNE MINEL-XHAHILINE
  11,47,KALE RABBI ‘INNI ‘A’UDHU BIKE ‘EN ‘ES’ELEKE MA LEJSE LI BIHI ‘ILMUN WE ‘ILLA TEGFIR LI WE TERHEMNI ‘EKUN MINEL-HASIRINE
  11,48,KILE JA NUHU EHBIT BISELAMIN MINNA WE BEREKATIN ‘ALEJKE WE ‘ALA ‘UMEMIN MIMMEN ME’AKE WE ‘UMEMUN SENUMETTI’UHUM THUMME JEMESSUHUM MINNA ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  11,49,TILKE MIN ‘ENBA’IL-GAJBI NUHIHA ‘ILEJKE MA KUNTE TA’LEMUHA ‘ENTE WE LA KAWMUKE MIN KABLI HADHA FASBIR ‘INNEL-’AKIBETE LILMUTTEKINE
  11,50,WE ‘ILA ‘ADIN ‘EHAHUM HUDÆN KALE JA KAWMI A’BUDU ELLAHE MA LEKUM MIN ‘ILEHIN GAJRUHU ‘IN ‘ENTUM ‘ILLA MUFTERUNE
  11,51,JA KAWMI LA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI ‘EXHRÆN ‘IN ‘EXHRIJE ‘ILLA ‘ALEL-LEDHI FETERENI ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  11,52,WE JA KAWMI ESTEGFIRU REBBEKUM THUMME TUBU ‘ILEJHI JURSILI ES-SEMA’E ‘ALEJKUM MIDRARÆN WE JEZIDKUM KUWETEN ‘ILA KUWETIKUM WE LA TETEWELLEW MUXHRIMINE
  11,53,KALU JA HUDU MA XHI’TENA BIBEJJINETIN WE MA NEHNU BITARIKI ‘ALIHETINA ‘AN KAWLIKE WE MA NEHNU LEKE BIMU’UMININE
  11,54,‘IN NEKULU ‘ILLA A’TERAKE BA’DU ‘ALIHETINA BISU’IN KALE ‘INNI ‘USH/HIDU ELLAHE WE ESH/HEDU ‘ENNI BERI’UN MIMMA TUSHRIKUNE
  11,55,MIN DUNIHI FEKIDUNI XHEMI’ÆN THUMME LA TUNDHIRUNI
  11,56,‘INNI TEWEKKELTU ‘ALA ELLAHI RABBI WE RABBIKUM MA MIN DABBETIN ‘ILLA HUWE ‘AHIDHUN BINASIJETIHA ‘INNE RABBI ‘ALA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  11,57,FE’IN TEWELLEW FEKAD ‘EBLEGTUKUM MA ‘URSILTU BIHI ‘ILEJKUM WE JESTEHLIFU RABBI KAWMÆN GAJREKUM WE LA TEDURRUNEHU SHEJ’ÆN ‘INNE RABBI ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN HEFIDHUN
  11,58,WE LEMMA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA NEXHXHEJNA HUDÆN WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ME’AHU BIREHMETIN MINNA WE NEXHXHEJNAHUM MIN ‘ADHABIN GALIDHIN
  11,59,WE TILKE ‘ADUN XHEHEDU BI’AJATI RABBIHIM WE ‘ASEW RUSULEHU WE ETTEBA’U ‘EMRE KULLI XHEBBARIN ‘ANIDIN
  11,60,WE ‘UTBI’U FI HEDHIHI ED-DUNJA LA’NETEN WE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘ELA ‘INNE ‘ADÆN KEFERU REBBEHUM ‘ELA BU’DÆN LI’ADIN KAWMI HUDIN
  11,61,WE ‘ILA THEMUDE ‘EHAHUM SALIHÆN KALE JA KAWMI A’BUDU ELLAHE MA LEKUM MIN ‘ILEHIN GAJRUHU HUWE ‘ENSHE’EKUM MINEL-’ERDI WE ESTA’MEREKUM FIHA FASTEGFIRUHU THUMME TUBU ‘ILEJHI ‘INNE RABBI KARIBUN MUXHIBUN
  11,62,KALU JA SALIHU KAD KUNTE FINA MERXHUWÆN KABLE HADHA ‘ETENHANA ‘EN NA’BUDE MA JA’BUDU ‘ABA’UUNA WE ‘INNENA LEFI SHEKKIN MIMMA TED’UNA ‘ILEJHI MURIBIN
  11,63,KALE JA KAWMI ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN KUNTU ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MIN RABBI WE ‘ATANI MINHU REHMETEN FEMEN JENSURUNI MINEL-LAHI ‘IN ‘ASEJTUHU FEMA TEZIDUNENI GAJRE TEHSIRIN
  11,64,WE JA KAWMI HEDHIHI NAKATU ELLAHI LEKUM ‘AJETEN FEDHERUHA TE’KUL FI ‘ERDI ELLAHI WE LA TEMESSUHA BISU’IN FEJE’HUDHEKUM ‘ADHABUN KARIBUN
  11,65,FE’AKARUHA FEKALE TEMETTA’U FI DARIKUM THELATHETE ‘EJJAMIN DHALIKE WA’DUN GAJRU MEKDHUBIN
  11,66,FELEMMA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA NEXHXHEJNA SALIHÆN WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ME’AHU BIREHMETIN MINNA WE MIN HIZJI JEWMI’IDHIN ‘INNE REBBEKE HUWEL-KAWIJUL-’AZIZU
  11,67,WE ‘EHADHEL-LEDHINE DHELEMU ES-SEJHETU FE’ESBEHU FI DIJARIHIM XHATHIMINE
  11,68,KE’EN LEM JEGNEW FIHA ‘ELA ‘INNE THEMUDE KEFERU REBBEHUM ‘ELA BU’DÆN LITHEMUDE
  11,69,WE LEKAD XHA’ET RUSULUNA ‘IBRAHIME BIL-BUSHRA KALU SELAMÆN KALE SELAMUN FEMA LEBITHE ‘EN XHA’E BI’IXHLIN HENIDHIN
  11,70,FELEMMA RE’A ‘EJDIJEHUM LA TESILU ‘ILEJHI NEKIREHUM WE ‘EWXHESE MINHUM HIFETEN KALU LA TEHAF ‘INNA ‘URSILNA ‘ILA KAWMI LUTIN
  11,71,WE EMRE’ETUHU KA’IMETUN FEDEHIKET FEBESHSHERNAHA BI’ISHAKA WE MIN WERA’I ‘ISHAKA JA’KUBE
  11,72,KALET JA WEJLETA ‘E’ELIDU WE ‘ENA ‘AXHUZUN WE HEDHA BA’LI SHEJHÆN ‘INNE HADHA LESHEJ’UN ‘AXHIBUN
  11,73,KALU ‘ETA’XHEBINE MIN ‘EMRI ELLAHI REHMETU ELLAHI WE BEREKATUHU ‘ALEJKUM ‘EHLEL-BEJTI ‘INNEHU HEMIDUN MEXHIDUN
  11,74,FELEMMA DHEHEBE ‘AN ‘IBRAHIME ER-REW’U WE XHA’ET/HUL-BUSHRA JUXHADILUNA FI KAWMI LUTIN
  11,75,‘INNE ‘IBRAHIME LEHELIMUN ‘EWWAHUN MUNIBUN
  11,76,JA ‘IBRAHIMU ‘A’RID ‘AN HADHA ‘INNEHU KAD XHA’E ‘EMRU RABBIKE WE ‘INNEHUM ‘ATIHIM ‘ADHABUN GAJRU MERDUDIN
  11,77,WE LEMMA XHA’ET RUSULUNA LUTÆN SI’E BIHIM WE DAKA BIHIM DHER’ÆN WE KALE HADHA JEWMUN ‘ASIBUN
  11,78,WE XHA’EHU KAWMUHU JUHRA’UNE ‘ILEJHI WE MIN KABLU KANU JA’MELUNE ES-SEJJI’ATI KALE JA KAWMI HA’UULA’ BENATI HUNNE ‘ETHERU LEKUM FE ETTEKU ELLAHE WE LA TUHZUNI FI DEJFI ‘ELEJSE MINKUM REXHULUN RESHIDUN
  11,79,KALU LEKAD ‘ALIMTE MA LENA FI BENATIKE MIN HEKKIN WE ‘INNEKE LETA’LEMU MA NURIDU
  11,80,KALE LEW ‘ENNE LI BIKUM KUWETEN ‘EW ‘AWI ‘ILA RUKNIN SHEDIDIN
  11,81,KALU JA LUTU ‘INNA RUSULU RABBIKE LEN JESILU ‘ILEJKE FE’ESRI BI’EHLIKE BIKIT’IN MINEL-LEJLI WE LA JELTEFIT MINKUM ‘EHEDUN ‘ILLA EMRE’ETEKE ‘INNEHU MUSIBUHA MA ‘ESABEHUM ‘INNE MEW’IDEHUMU ES-SUBHU ‘ELEJSE ES-SUBHU BIKARIBIN
  11,82,FELEMMA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA XHE’ALNA ‘ALIJEHA SAFILEHA WE ‘EMTERNA ‘ALEJHA HIXHARETEN MIN SIXHXHILIN MENDUDIN
  11,83,MUSEWWEMETEN ‘INDE RABBIKE WE MA HIJE MINE EDH-DHALIMINE BIBA’IDIN
  11,84,WE ‘ILA MEDJENE ‘EHAHUM SHU’AJBÆN KALE JA KAWMI A’BUDU ELLAHE MA LEKUM MIN ‘ILEHIN GAJRUHU WE LA TENKUSUL-MIKJA LE WEL-MIZANE ‘INNI ‘ERAKUM BIHAJRIN WE ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘ALEJKUM ‘ADHABE JEWMIN MUHITIN
  11,85,WE JA KAWMI ‘EWFUL-MIKJALE WEL-MIZANE BIL-KISTI WE LA TEBHASU EN-NASE ‘ESHJA’EHUM WE LA TA’THEW FIL-’ERDI MUFSIDINE
  11,86,BEKIJETU ELLAHI HAJRUN LEKUM ‘IN KUNTUM MU’UMININE WE MA ‘ENA ‘ALEJKUM BIHEFIDHIN
  11,87,KALU JA SHU’AJBU ‘ESELATUKE TE’MURUKE ‘EN NETRUKE MA JA’BUDU ‘ABA’UUNA ‘EW ‘EN NEF’ALE FI ‘EMWALINA MA NESHA’U ‘INNEKE LE’ENTEL-HELIMU ER-RESHIDU
  11,88,KALE JA KAWMI ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN KUNTU ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MIN RABBI WE REZEKANI MINHU RIZKÆN HESENÆN WE MA ‘URIDU ‘EN ‘UHALIFEKUM ‘ILA MA ‘ENHAKUM ‘ANHU ‘IN ‘URIDU ‘ILLAL-’ISLAHE MA ESTETA’TU WE MA TEWFIKI ‘ILLA BILLAHI ‘ALEJHI TEWEKKELTU WE ‘ILEJHI ‘UNIBU
  11,89,WE JA KAWMI LA JEXHRIMENNEKUM SHIKAKI ‘EN JUSIBEKUM MITHLU MA ‘ESABE KAWME NUHIN ‘EW KAWME HUDIN ‘EW KAWME SALIHIN WE MA KAWMU LUTIN MINKUM BIBA’IDIN
  11,90,WE ESTEGFIRU REBBEKUM THUMME TUBU ‘ILEJHI ‘INNE RABBI REHIMUN WEDUDUN
  11,91,KALU JA SHU’AJBU MA NEFKAHU KETHIRÆN MIMMA TEKULU WE ‘INNA LENERAKE FINA DA’IFÆN WE LEWLA REHTUKE LEREXHEMNAKE WE MA ‘ENTE ‘ALEJNA BI’AZIZIN
  11,92,KALE JA KAWMI ‘EREHTI ‘E’AZZU ‘ALEJKUM MINEL-LAHI WE ETTEHADHTUMUHU WERA’EKUM DHIHRIJÆN ‘INNE RABBI BIMA TA’MELUNE MUHITUN
  11,93,WE JA KAWMI A’MELU ‘ALA MEKANETIKUM ‘INNI ‘AMILUN SEWFE TA’LEMUNE MEN JE’TIHI ‘ADHABUN JUHZIHI WE MEN HUWE KADHIBUN WE ERTEKIBU ‘INNI ME’AKUM REKIBUN
  11,94,WE LEMMA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA NEXHXHEJNA SHU’AJBÆN WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ME’AHU BIREHMETIN MINNA WE ‘EHADHETIL-LEDHINE DHELEMU ES-SEJHETU FE’ESBEHU FI DIJARIHIM XHATHIMINE
  11,95,KE’EN LEM JEGNEW FIHA ‘ELA BU’DÆN LIMEDJENE KEMA BA’IDET THEMUDU
  11,96,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA MUSA BI’AJATINA WE SULTANIN MUBININ
  11,97,‘ILA FIR’AWNE WE MELE’IHI FE ETTEBA’U ‘EMRE FIR’AWNE WE MA ‘EMRU FIR’AWNE BIRESHIDIN
  11,98,JEKDUMU KAWMEHU JEWMEL-KIJAMETI FE’EWREDEHUMU EN-NARE WE BI’SEL-WIRDUL-MEWRUDU
  11,99,WE ‘UTBI’U FI HEDHIHI LA’NETEN WE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI BI’SE ER-RIFDUL-MERFUDU
  11,100,DHALIKE MIN ‘ENBA’IL-KURA NEKUSSUHU ‘ALEJKE MINHA KA’IMUN WE HESIDUN
  11,101,WE MA DHELEMNAHUM WE LEKIN DHELEMU ‘ENFUSEHUM FEMA ‘EGNET ‘ANHUM ‘ALIHETUHUMU ELLETI JED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI MIN SHEJ’IN LEMMA XHA’E ‘EMRU RABBIKE WE MA ZADUHUM GAJRE TETBIBIN
  11,102,WE KEDHELIKE ‘EHDHU RABBIKE ‘IDHA ‘EHADHEL-KURA WE HIJE DHALIMETUN ‘INNE ‘EHDHEHU ‘ELIMUN SHEDIDUN
  11,103,‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIMEN HAFE ‘ADHABEL-’AHIRETI DHALIKE JEWMUN MEXHMU’UN LEHU EN-NASU WE DHELIKE JEWMUN MESH/HUDUN
  11,104,WE MA NU’UEHHIRUHU ‘ILLA LI’XHELIN MA’DUDIN
  11,105,JEWME JE’TI LA TEKELLEMU NEFSUN ‘ILLA BI’IDHNIHI FEMINHUM SHEKIJUN WE SA’IDUN
  11,106,FE’EMMAL-LEDHINE SHEKU FEFI EN-NARI LEHUM FIHA ZEFIRUN WE SHEHIKUN
  11,107,HALIDINE FIHA MA DAMETI ES-SEMAWATU WEL-’ERDU ‘ILLA MA SHA’E REBBUKE ‘INNE REBBEKE FA’’ALUN LIMA JURIDU
  11,108,WE ‘EMMAL-LEDHINE SU’IDU FEFIL-XHENNETI HALIDINE FIHA MA DAMETI ES-SEMAWATU WEL-’ERDU ‘ILLA MA SHA’E REBBUKE ‘ATA’EN GAJRE MEXHDHUDHIN
  11,109,FELA TEKU FI MIRJETIN MIMMA JA’BUDU HA’UULA’ MA JA’BUDUNE ‘ILLA KEMA JA’BUDU ‘ABA’UUHUM MIN KABLU WE ‘INNA LEMUWEFFUHUM NESIBEHUM GAJRE MENKUSIN
  11,110,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA MUSAL-KITABE FAHTULIFE FIHI WE LEWLA KELIMETUN SEBEKAT MIN RABBIKE LEKUDIJE BEJNEHUM WE ‘INNEHUM LEFI SHEKKIN MINHU MURIBIN
  11,111,WE ‘INNE KULLA LEMMA LEJUWEFFIJENNEHUM REBBUKE ‘A’MALEHUM ‘INNEHU BIMA JA’MELUNE HABIRUN
  11,112,FASTEKIM KEMA ‘UMIRTE WE MEN TABE ME’AKE WE LA TETGAW ‘INNEHU BIMA TA’MELUNE BESIRUN
  11,113,WE LA TERKENU ‘ILAL-LEDHINE DHELEMU FETEMESSEKUMU EN-NARU WE MA LEKUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI MIN ‘EWLIJA’E THUMME LA TUNSERUNE
  11,114,WE ‘EKIMI ES-SELÆTE TEREFEJI EN-NEHARI WE ZULEFÆN MINEL-LEJLI ‘INNEL-HESENATI JUDH/HIBNE ES-SEJJI’ATI DHALIKE DHIKRA LILDHDHAKIRINE
  11,115,WE ESBIR FE’INNALL-LLAHE LA JUDI’U ‘EXHREL-MUHSININE
  11,116,FELEWLA KANE MINEL-KURUNI MIN KABLIKUM ‘ULU BEKIJETIN JENHEWNE ‘ANIL-FESADI FIL-’ERDI ‘ILLA KALILÆN MIMMEN ‘ENXHEJNA MINHUM WE ETTEBE’AL-LEDHINE DHELEMU MA ‘UTRIFU FIHI WE KANU MUXHRIMINE
  11,117,WE MA KANE REBBUKE LIJUHLIKEL-KURA BIDHULMIN WE ‘EHLUHA MUSLIHUNE
  11,118,WE LEW SHA’E REBBUKE LEXHE’ALE EN-NASE ‘UMMETEN WAHIDETEN WE LA JEZALUNE MUHTELIFINE
  11,119,‘ILLA MEN REHIME REBBUKE WE LIDHELIKE HALEKAHUM WE TEMMET KELIMETU RABBIKE LE’EMLE’ENNE XHEHENNEME MINEL-XHINNETI WE EN-NASI ‘EXHMA’INE
  11,120,WE KULLÆN NEKUSSU ‘ALEJKE MIN ‘ENBA’I ER-RUSULI MA NUTHEBBITU BIHI FU’UADEKE WE XHA’EKE FI HEDHIHIL-HEKKU WE MEW’IDHETUN WE DHIKRA LILMU’UMININE
  11,121,WE KUL LILLEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE A’MELU ‘ALA MEKANETIKUM ‘INNA ‘AMILUNE
  11,122,WE ENTEDHIRU ‘INNA MUNTEDHIRUNE
  11,123,WE LILLEHI GAJBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE ‘ILEJHI JURXHA’UL-’EMRU KULLUHU FA’BUD/HU WE TEWEKKEL ‘ALEJHI WE MA REBBUKE BIGAFILIN ‘AMMA TA’MELUNE
  12,1,‘ELIF-LAM-RA TILKE ‘AJATUL-KITABIL-MUBINI
  12,2,‘INNA ‘ENZELNAHU KUR’ANÆN ‘AREBIJÆN LE’ALLEKUM TA’KILUNE
  12,3,NEHNU NEKUSSU ‘ALEJKE ‘EHSENEL-KASESI BIMA ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJKE HADHAL-KUR’ANE WE ‘IN KUNTE MIN KABLIHI LEMINEL-GAFILINE
  12,4,‘IDH KALE JUSUFU LI’EBIHI JA ‘EBETI ‘INNI RE’EJTU ‘EHEDE ‘ASHERE KEWKEBÆN WE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE RE’EJTUHUM LI SAXHIDINE
  12,5,KALE JA BUNEJJE LA TEKSUS RU’UJA KE ‘ALA ‘IHWETIKE FEJEKIDU LEKE KEJDÆN ‘INNE ESH-SHEJTANE LIL’INSANI ‘ADUWUN MUBINUN
  12,6,WE KEDHELIKE JEXHTEBIKE REBBUKE WE JU’ALLIMUKE MIN TE’WILIL-’EHADITHI WE JUTIMMU NI’METEHU ‘ALEJKE WE ‘ALA ‘ALI JA’KUBE KEMA ‘ETEMMEHA ‘ALA ‘EBEWEJKE MIN KABLU ‘IBRAHIME WE ‘ISHAKA ‘INNE REBBEKE ‘ALIMUN HEKIMUN
  12,7,LEKAD KANE FI JUSUFE WE ‘IHWETIHI ‘AJATUN LILSSA’ILINE
  12,8,‘IDH KALU LEJUSUFU WE ‘EHUHU ‘EHEBBU ‘ILA ‘EBINA MINNA WE NEHNU ‘USBETUN ‘INNE ‘EBANA LEFI DELALIN MUBININ
  12,9,EKTULU JUSUFE ‘EWI ETREHUHU ‘ERDÆN JEHLU LEKUM WEXHHU ‘EBIKUM WE TEKUNU MIN BA’DIHI KAWMÆN SALIHINE
  12,10,KALE KA’ILUN MINHUM LA TEKTULU JUSUFE WE ‘ELKUHU FI GAJABETIL-XHUBBI JELTEKITHU BA’DU ES-SEJJARETI ‘IN KUNTUM FA’ILINE
  12,11,KALU JA ‘EBANA MA LEKE LA TE’MENNA ‘ALA JUSUFE WE ‘INNA LEHU LENASIHUNE
  12,12,‘ERSILHU ME’ANA GADÆN JERTA’ WE JEL’AB WE ‘INNA LEHU LEHAFIDHUNE
  12,13,KALE ‘INNI LEJEHZUNUNI ‘EN TEDH/HEBU BIHI WE ‘EHAFU ‘EN JE’KULEHU EDH-DHI’BU WE ‘ENTUM ‘ANHU GAFILUNE
  12,14,KALU LE’IN ‘EKELEHU EDH-DHI’BU WE NEHNU ‘USBETUN ‘INNA ‘IDHÆN LEHASIRUNE
  12,15,FELEMMA DHEHEBU BIHI WE ‘EXHMA’U ‘EN JEXH’ALUHU FI GAJABETIL-XHUBBI WE ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJHI LETUNEBBI’ENNEHUM BI’EMRIHIM HADHA WE HUM LA JESH’URUNE
  12,16,WE XHA’U ‘EBAHUM ‘ISHA’EN JEBKUNE
  12,17,KALU JA ‘EBANA ‘INNA DHEHEBNA NESTEBIKU WE TEREKNA JUSUFE ‘INDE META’INA FE’EKELEHU EDH-DHI’BU WE MA ‘ENTE BIMU’UMININ LENA WE LEW KUNNA SADIKINE
  12,18,WE XHA’U ‘ALA KAMISIHI BIDEMIN KEDHIBIN KALE BEL SEWWELET LEKUM ‘ENFUSUKUM ‘EMRÆN FESEBRUN XHEMILUN WEL-LAHUL-MUSTA’ANU ‘ALA MA TESIFUNE
  12,19,WE XHA’ET SEJJARETUN FE’ERSELU WE ERIDEHUM FE’EDLA DELWEHU KALE JA BUSHRA HADHA GULAMUN WE ‘ESERRUHU BIDA’ATEN WEL-LAHU ‘ALIMUN BIMA JA’MELUNE
  12,20,WE SHEREWHU BITHEMENIN BEHSIN DERAHIME MA’DUDETIN WE KANU FIHI MINE EZ-ZAHIDINE
  12,21,WE KALEL-LEDHI ESHTERAHU MIN MISRE LI’IMRE’ETIHI ‘EKRIMI METHWAHU ‘ASA ‘EN JENFE’ANA ‘EW NETTEHIDHEHU WELEDÆN WE KEDHELIKE MEKKENNA LIJUSUFE FIL-’ERDI WE LINU’ALLIMEHU MIN TE’WILIL-’EHADITHI WEL-LAHU GALIBUN ‘ALA ‘EMRIHI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’
  12,22,WE LEMMA BELEGA ‘ESHUDDEHU ‘ATEJNAHU HUKMÆN WE ‘ILMÆN WE KEDHELIKE NEXHZIL-MUHSININE
  12,23,WE RAWEDET/HU ELLETI HUWE FI BEJTIHA ‘AN NEFSIHI WE GALLEKATIL-’EBWABE WE KALET HEJTE LEKE KALE MA’ADHEL-LAHI ‘INNEHU RABBI ‘EHSENE METHWAJE ‘INNEHU LA JUFLIHU EDH-DHALIMUNE
  12,24,WE LEKAD HEMMET BIHI WE HEMME BIHA LEWLA ‘EN RE’A BURHANE RABBIHI KEDHALIKE LINESRIFE ‘ANHU ES-SU’E WEL-FEHSHA’E ‘INNEHU MIN ‘IBADINAL-MUHLESINE
  12,25,WE ESTEBEKAL-BABE WE KADDET KAMISEHU MIN DUBURIN WE ‘ELFEJA SEJJIDEHA LEDAL-BABI KALET MA XHEZA’U MEN ‘ERADE BI’EHLIKE SU’ÆN ‘ILLA ‘EN JUSXHENE ‘EW ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  12,26,KALE HIJE RAWEDETNI ‘AN NEFSI WE SHEHIDE SHAHIDUN MIN ‘EHLIHA ‘IN KANE KAMISUHU KUDDE MIN KUBULIN FESEDEKAT WE HUWE MINEL-KADHIBINE
  12,27,WE ‘IN KANE KAMISUHU KUDDE MIN DUBURIN FEKEDHEBET WE HUWE MINE ES-SADIKINE
  12,28,FELEMMA RE’A KAMISEHU KUDDE MIN DUBURIN KALE ‘INNEHU MIN KEJDIKUNNE ‘INNE KEJDEKUNNE ‘ADHIMUN
  12,29,JUSUFU ‘A’RID ‘AN HADHA WE ESTEGFIRI LIDHENBIKI ‘INNEKI KUNTI MINEL-HATI’INE
  12,30,WE KALE NISWETUN FIL-MEDINETI EMRE’ETUL-’AZIZI TURAWIDU FETAHA ‘AN NEFSIHI KAD SHEGAFEHA HUBBÆN ‘INNA LENERAHA FI DELALIN MUBININ
  12,31,FELEMMA SEMI’AT BIMEKRIHINNE ‘ERSELET ‘ILEJHINNE WE ‘A’TEDET LEHUNNE MUTTEKE’EN WE ‘ATET KULLE WAHIDETIN MINHUNNE SIKKINÆN WE KALETI EHRUXH ‘ALEJHINNE FELEMMA RE’EJNEHU ‘EKBERNEHU WE KATTA’NE ‘EJDIJEHUNNE WE KULNE HASHE LILLAHI MA HADHA BESHERÆN ‘IN HADHA
  12,32,KALET FEDHALIKUNNEL-LEDHI LUMTUNNENI FIHI WE LEKAD RAWEDTTUHU ‘AN NEFSIHI FASTA’SEME WE LE’IN LEM JEF’AL MA ‘AMURUHU LEJUSXHENENNE WE LEJEKUNÆN MINE ES-SAGIRINE
  12,33,KALE RABBI ES-SIXHNU ‘EHEBBU ‘ILEJJE MIMMA JED’UNENI ‘ILEJHI WE ‘ILLA TESRIF ‘ANNI KEJDEHUNNE ‘ESBU ‘ILEJHINNE WE ‘EKUN MINEL-XHAHILINE
  12,34,FASTEXHABE LEHU REBBUHU FESEREFE ‘ANHU KEJDEHUNNE ‘INNEHU HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-’ALIMU
  12,35,THUMME BEDA LEHUM MIN BA’DI MA RE’EWL-’AJATI LEJESXHUNUNNEHU HETTA HININ
  12,36,WE DEHALE ME’AHU ES-SIXHNE FETEJANI KALE ‘EHEDUHUMA ‘INNI ‘ERANI ‘A’SIRU HAMRÆN WE KALEL-’AHARU ‘INNI ‘ERANI ‘EHMILU FEWKA RE’SI HUBZÆN TE’KULUT-TEJRU MINHU NEBBI’NA BITE’WILIHI ‘INNA NERAKE MINEL-MUHSININE
  12,37,KALE LA JE’TIKUMA TA’AMUN TURZEKANIHI ‘ILLA NEBBE’TUKUMA BITE’WILIHI KABLE ‘EN JE’TIJEKUMA DHALIKUMA MIMMA ‘ALLEMENI RABBI ‘INNI TEREKTU MILLETE KAWMIN LA JU’UMINUNE BILLAHI WE HUM BIL-’AHIRETI HUM KAFIRUNE
  12,38,WE ETTEBA’TU MILLETE ‘ABA’I ‘IBRAHIME WE ‘ISHAKA WE JA’KUBE MA KANE LENA ‘EN NUSHRIKE BILLAHI MIN SHEJ’IN DHALIKE MIN FEDLI ELLAHI ‘ALEJNA WE ‘ALA EN-NASI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JESHKURUNE
  12,39,JA SAHIBEJI ES-SIXHNI ‘E’ERBABUN MUTEFERRIKUNE HAJRUN ‘EMI ELLAHUL-WAHIDUL-KAHHARU
  12,40,MA TA’BUDUNE MIN DUNIHI ‘ILLA ‘ESMA’EN SEMMEJTUMUHA ‘ENTUM WE ‘ABA’UUKUM MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU BIHA MIN SULTANIN ‘INIL-HUKMU ‘ILLA LILLAHI ‘EMERE ‘ELLA TA’BUDU ‘ILLA ‘IJAHU DHALIKE ED-DINUL-KAJJIMU WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’LEMUNE
  12,41,JA SAHIBEJI ES-SIXHNI ‘EMMA ‘EHEDUKUMA FEJESKI REBBEHU HAMRÆN WE ‘EMMAL-’AHARU FEJUSLEBU FETE’KULUT-TEJRU MIN RE’SIHI KUDIJEL-’EMRUL-LEDHI FIHI TESTEFTIJANI
  12,42,WE KALE LILLEDHI DHENNE ‘ENNEHU NAXHIN MINHUMA EDHKURNI ‘INDE RABBIKE FE’ENSAHU ESH-SHEJTANU DHIKRE RABBIHI FELEBITHE FI ES-SIXHNI BID’A SININE
  12,43,WE KALEL-MELIKU ‘INNI ‘ERA SEB’A BEKARATIN SIMANIN JE’KULUHUNNE SEB’UN ‘IXHAFUN WE SEB’A SUNBULATIN HUDRIN WE ‘UHARE JA BISATIN JA ‘EJJUHAL-MELE’U ‘EFTUNI FI RU’UJA JE ‘IN KUNTUM LILRRU’UJA TA’BURUNE
  12,44,KALU ‘EDGATHU ‘EHLAMIN WE MA NEHNU BITE’WILIL-’EHLAMI BI’ALIMINE
  12,45,WE KALEL-LEDHI NEXHA MINHUMA WE EIDDEKERE BA’DE ‘UMMETIN ‘ENA ‘UNEBBI’UKUM BITE’WILIHI FE’ERSILUNI
  12,46,JUSUFU ‘EJJUHA ES-SIDDIKU ‘EFTINA FI SEB’I BEKARATIN SIMANIN JE’KULUHUNNE SEB’UN ‘IXHAFUN WE SEB’I SUNBULATIN HUDRIN WE ‘UHARE JA BISATIN LE’ALLI ‘ERXHI’U ‘ILA EN-NASI LE’ALLEHUM JA’LEMUNE
  12,47,KALE TEZRA’UNE SEB’A SININE DE’EBÆN FEMA HESEDTUM FEDHERUHU FI SUNBULIHI ‘ILLA KALILÆN MIMMA TE’KULUNE
  12,48,THUMME JE’TI MIN BA’DI DHALIKE SEB’UN SHIDADUN JE’KULNE MA KADDEMTUM LEHUNNE ‘ILLA KALILÆN MIMMA TUHSINUNE
  12,49,THUMME JE’TI MIN BA’DI DHALIKE ‘AMUN FIHI JUGATHU EN-NASU WE FIHI JA’SIRUNE
  12,50,WE KALEL-MELIKU E’TUNI BIHI FELEMMA XHA’EHU ER-RESULU KALE ERXHI’ ‘ILA RABBIKE FAS’ELHU MA BALU EN-NISWETIL-LATI KATTA’NE ‘EJDIJEHUNNE ‘INNE RABBI BIKEJDIHINNE ‘ALIMUN
  12,51,KALE MA HATBUKUNNE ‘IDH RAWEDTTUNNE JUSUFE ‘AN NEFSIHI KULNE HASHE LILLAHI MA ‘ALIMNA ‘ALEJHI MIN SU’IN KALETI EMRE’ETUL-’AZIZIL-’ANE HESHESEL-HEKKU ‘ENA RAWEDTTUHU ‘AN NEFSIHI WE ‘INNEHU LEMINE ES-SADIKINE
  12,52,DHALIKE LIJA’LEME ‘ENNI LEM ‘EHUNHU BIL-GAJBI WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE LA JEHDI KEJDEL-HA’ININE